interact with this effect accordingly.£6/15/2010: In a Two-Headed Giant game, Celestial Mantle’s essentially doubles the team’s life total. Specifically, the triggered ability will affect one player’s life total, and then the team’s life total is adjusted by the amount of life the player gains as a result of this ability. Suppose a creature enchanted by Celestial Mantle deals combat damage to an opponent, and that creature’s controller’s team has 11 life. That player then has 11 life, so it’s doubled to 22, for a net gain of 11 life. The team’s life total becomes 22 (11 + 11).','W',NULL,'2.5','3.75','6.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W','天界披风',NULL,'Manteau céleste','Himmlischer Mantel','Manto Celestiale','天界のマントル','Manto Celestial','Небесная Мантия','Manto celestial',NULL,'结界～灵气',NULL,'Enchantement : aura','Verzauberung — Aura','Incantesimo — Aura','エンチャント ― オーラ','Encantamento — Aura','Чары — Аура','Encantamiento — Aura',NULL,'结附于生物£所结附的生物得+3/+3。£每当所结附的生物对牌手造成战斗伤害时，将其操控者的总生命加倍。',NULL,'Enchanter : créature£La créature enchantée gagne +3/+3.£À chaque fois que la créature enchantée inflige des blessures de combat à un joueur, doublez le total de points de vie de son contrôleur.','Kreaturenverzauberung£Die verzauberte Kreatur erhält +3/+3.£Immer wenn die verzauberte Kreatur einem Spieler Kampfschaden zufügt, verdoppele die Lebenspunkte ihres Beherrschers.','Incanta creatura£La creatura incantata prende +3/+3.£Ogniqualvolta la creatura incantata infligge danno da combattimento a un giocatore, raddoppia i punti vita del suo controllore.','エンチャント（クリーチャー）£エンチャントされているクリーチャーは＋３/＋３の修整を受ける。£エンチャントされているクリーチャーがいずれかのプレイヤーに戦闘ダメージを与えるたび、それのコントローラーのライフの総量を２倍にする。','Encantar criatura£A criatura encantada recebe +3/+3.£Toda vez que a criatura encantada causar dano de combate a um jogador, duplique o total de pontos de vida de seu controlador.','Зачаровать существо£Зачарованное существо получает +3/+3.£Каждый раз, когда зачарованное существо наносит боевые повреждения игроку, удвойте количество жизней контролирующего его игрока.','Encantar criatura.£La criatura encantada obtiene +3/+3.£Siempre que la criatura encantada haga daño de combate a un jugador, duplica el total de vidas de su controlador.',NULL,'#_有了此铠甲，就连高山也无需畏惧。_#',NULL,'#_Une montagne se fracasserait sur une telle armure._#','#_Unter solch einer Rüstung würde sogar ein Berg zusammenbrechen._#','#_Su una tale armatura, perfino una montagna si spezzerebbe._#','#_こんな鎧があれば、山でさえ砕け散る。_#','#_Com uma armadura assim, até mesmo uma montanha se parte._#','#_Об такие доспехи разбилась бы даже гора._#','#_Contra esa armadura, hasta una montaña se quebraría._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('195402','Chandra Ablaze','ZEN','Legendary Planeswalker — Chandra','M','{4}{R}{R}','6',NULL,NULL,'5','+1: Discard a card. If a red card is discarded this way, Chandra Ablaze deals 4 damage to any target.£−2: Each player discards their hand, then draws three cards.£−7: Cast any number of red instant and/or sorcery cards from your graveyard without paying their mana costs.',NULL,NULL,'Steve Argyle','120','3.98','£10/1/2009: If you activate Chandra Ablaze’s first ability, you don’t discard a card until the ability resolves. You may activate the ability even if your hand is empty. You choose a target as you activate the ability even if you have no red cards in hand at that time.£10/1/2009: As the first ability resolves, nothing happens if your hand is empty. But if you have any cards in hand, you must discard one. If you discard a nonred card, Chandra doesn’t deal any damage.£10/1/2009: If the creature targeted by the first ability is an illegal target by the time it resolves, the entire ability doesn’t resolve. You won’t discard a card.£10/1/2009: You may activate Chandra’s second ability even if your hand is empty. As it resolves, a player whose hand is empty simply draws three cards.£10/1/2009: You cast red instant cards and red sorcery cards from your graveyard as part of the resolu